Serpentor:



Serpentor flew through the air, managing to land on a foot and keep his 
balance.  But he felt sharp pains run up the leg he landed on.  He grunted, 
taking a step forward that resulted in a burst of pain in his leg.  He 
cursed, seeing the Alliance and Maxis stop shooting at each other.

He kept his optic sensors powered up, just in case, training them on 
Lunaprine and waiting.
